  "instructions": [
    "Combine dried ancho chillies and 2 cups of hot water in a bowl. Let it steep for 20 minutes.",
    "Heat sesame oil in a large pot over medium heat. Add ginger and saut\u007f until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "Add cinnamon and star anise to the pot. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add vegetable broth to the pot. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add nuka-pickle and rice noodles to the pot. Cook for 8-10 minutes, or until noodles are tender.",
    "Stir in bean sprouts. Cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped cilantro and a lime wedge on the side."
  ],
